NOTES

- This is the version 0.4.0 of Mandriva Package Manager, MPM.
- Currently it has only package search (and filters) capabilities.
  No install/remove/update is available yet.
- The History, Settings, Install, Remove and Upgrade buttons
  do not do anything yet.
- Click an item to mark it for intallation/removal/upgrade. Click again to
  go back (or use the back button).
- You can control the splitter when an item is marked. In this mode, you
  may choose other items while keeping the buttons visible.

  If you find something wrong, just let us know.
  Thanks,
  Paulo - paulo@mandriva.com

HOW TO INSTALL AND RUN

- on Mandriva, install the package mpm
- run the command: mpm

